Question: Google invites you for a job interview. How do you prepare?
Answer:
First of all I prepare myself by anticipating the questions the employer might ask. I train myself by answering them alone and out loud. Secondly, I chose my best costume and cologne to impress the employer and give him a good impression. Finally, I make sure to know perfectly what I wrote in my resume and my motivation letter in order to answer his interrogations if any. 